metadata.name: Targa Florio 2022 | #20
metadata.description:
The Targa Florio was an event I’ve only heard legendary things about before.  
Now, I can finally confirm those things I’ve heard were true;  
The enthusiasm of the drivers, the heartwarming love of the locals, the breathtaking Sicilian landscapes (not to mention the food) and the unpredictable weather are just few of the things that make this event unique.  
I loved every single minute of this experience and despite how trivial it may sound, I genuinely can’t wait to do it again.  
Arrivederci Sicilia!

Targa Florio 2022 | #20  
Sicily, Italy - 14/10/2022  
Medium: Digital  
Edition: 1/1
